      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686be6968a81f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686be719defac.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686b538ba2c6c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686b5344df2ae.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686b500358c1f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686bec2bf2ad0.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686b54e28fee7.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686b5510d1b72.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686b4ffa12e90.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686b54b179277.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686beb7545209.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686b5002b1236.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686b50044d783.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686becfab3e46.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686b56602a954.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686b558c10952.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686be73395ff9.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686b577c72dff.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686b57af5d26e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686b5489c06cf.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686b568dee9b8.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686b5720a6822.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686bed5365d2c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686c46af7aaa7.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686be74e53c58.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686bec4e8057c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686b570a947b8.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686b500284d2d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686bebfe85245.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686b546c05452.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686c468d60ccd.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686b56327c721.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686c46d443208.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686be78d2afb3.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686b543a2b2f4.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686bec8ecbb32.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686becd0dbee9.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686beb9359a53.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686b4ff7c69f0.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686b55257f8d8.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/686b5617ae237.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; 1.0.0&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;1.0.0 is now out! Featuring the highly requested alternate version of the mod that brings the surface and sky levels back to the original of the game. A couple of new biomes have been added as well! Please select which version fits best for your preferences.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Normal - Reduced fog overall. Gives the game a much cleaner, and more vibrant look. Some LOD issues can be noticed however since the fog does hide background pop-in. Surface is much more visible from the sky, and background elements from the surface can be seen much easier. This version also features a seamless transition from the sky to the surface while skydiving.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Increased Fog - Brings the fog levels of the game back to the original. These changes do not affect the cave and depths, which have custom fog levels set. This is for those who prefer the original fog, or consider the masking of the LOD issues a priority over giving the game a clearer look. All custom biomes are still included in this version, so you can appreciate them with the original levels of fog present throughout the game.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Overhaul&lt;/em&gt;: Added a new version of the mod with increased fog bringing the fog levels back to the original game's while still retaining all of the new custom biomes. Excludes caves and depths.&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Addition&lt;/em&gt;: New custom biome in the corrupted Rito region pre-dungeon. Features a new daytime and nighttime atmosphere with more realistic lighting.&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Adjustment&lt;/em&gt;: Updated pre-dungeon Gerudo Desert sandstorm atmosphere.&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Adjustment&lt;/em&gt;: Small shrine atmosphere fix.&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;Tired of not being able to appreciate the beauty of Hyrule? This mod is not a reshade, rather, a reworking of most of the visual palettes in the game. Most areas in the game are heavily cleaned up with reduced fog, more vibrant colors, and unique biomes all across the map that compliment the areas they are representing. Nights are now darker, and much more atmospheric and moody but not to the point where you can't see. The sky, surface, caves and depths all have major visual changes, including brand new, custom day and night cycles. New cycles are added to Hyrule Field, Faron, Eldin, Lanayru, Hebra, Gerudo, Hyrule Castle and much more!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Sky - heavily reduced base fog so the surface is much clearer and more visible. Many areas have matching sky and surface environments, so the skydiving transition is seamless!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Surface - 10+ brand new custom day and night cycles all throughout the map with tons of variety. Even grassy climates have variety between them. Enjoy a blood moon styled Hyrule Castle, a winter wonderland Hebra, and an aquatic Lanayru, just to name a few. Even some existing areas that didn't need much modification, such as Korok Forest, have brand new morning and evening palettes! Expect new day/night cycles in Hyrule Field, Hebra, Eldin, Gerudo, Lanayru, Faron, Akkala, and much more! Some areas like Korok Forest and Gerudo Desert maintain fog to preserve their original atmosphere.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Caves - now defogged, and feature some modified colors.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="SelectedElement"&gt;Depths - features Vanilla+ work I did for Depths of the Kingdom mod by PotatoFried17 (linked down below). 10+ new biomes in the depths, mapped to different regions. Use with Depths of the Kingdom for an enhanced experience. Hebra is now cold in the depths with a chilly atmosphere, Eldin is even more fiery and dangerous, Gerudo is hot and arid, with many other regional changes included including the final dungeon area in the game!&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br&gt;Compatibility: Works on Switch and Emulator. Tested on Game Version 1.2.1. Works with most mods that do not edit EnvPalette.pack, Bootup.Nin_NX_NVN.pack, CavePalette.pack, and EnvPaletteTimeTable.pack.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This mod is compatible with Depths of the Kingdom by PotatoFried17, but TKMM MUST be used and Depths of the Kingdom must be placed higher than Hyrule: Rebeautified in the merge order. Abyssal climates (also created by me) can be used this way in the depths in conjunction with this mod. This mod can also be used with Challenge Mode this way. Highly recommended to use these mods together. Please give Depths of the Kingdom a download here: https://gamebanana.com/mods/578624&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Please note that development of this mod is not finished! I did extensive testing to make sure there were no visual artifacts or blatant errors. However, with how much content there is in this game, something may have slipped the cracks. Please report any issues in the comments below, and I am happy to address them. Some cutscenes use a unique environment that was not easy to figure out, and you may see fog in them that you do not normally see in the environment. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;For future plans for this mod, I do plan on possibly adding 1-2 more biomes to the depths, and for sure I plan on releasing a TKCL. Some options I plan to include are:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Brighter nights&lt;br&gt;- More fog&lt;br&gt;- Completely removed fog&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/hyrule_rebeautified_100_normal.zip" type="application/zip"/>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/hyrule_rebeautified_100_increased_fog.zip" type="application/zip"/>
      <category>Visual Overhaul</category>
      <category>Visual Overhaul</category>
