      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6480e18e1737c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/64793454e4f10.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6479345b60e17.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/64793460f1bfe.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6479346665165.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6479347c8c5bf.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/647934811c94d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/647934bd1802f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/647934c176991.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/647934d1e3899.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6479aed57b7d9.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/647934e5b43db.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6479aebda1601.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/647934f27b624.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/647934f6951a6.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/647934fa8e070.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/647934fe602b3.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/64793501c58e2.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/647935060b694.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6479350a2aa61.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6479350dd25d4.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/647935111a949.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/64793514a72f1.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/647935182c9f5.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6479351b5d409.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6479351ef3345.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/64793522673f8.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/64793525e16fc.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/647bd790ab82b.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/647bd796715be.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6480dcc298d29.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6480dcc7359b6.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6480dccd2d688.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6480dcd086a7e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6480dcd5bfa5d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6480dcd96140f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Game Version 1.4.0+&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Defogger should work on any update of the game.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Interior Addon may not.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You can try, let people know in the comments.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If it's determined that the Interior Add-on is broken for 1.4.0+, I will try to update it, but I can't make any promises.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;Not a ReShade nor is it related to ReShade.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;A native attempt at reducing the game's oppressive fog to aid with visibility and color.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Does not require an RSTB Edit.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Not compatible with any mods that alter:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;EnvPalette.pack.zs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;CavePalette.pack.zs&lt;/span&gt; (removable if you want vanilla cave fog.)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Bootup.Nin_NX_NVN.pack.zs&lt;/span&gt; (if you're using the Interior Add-on.)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;I will not make custom version of this mod or troubleshoot issues you have with mods that conflict with the above files.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;Image Slider Comparisons&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Comparisons of Vanilla against the Defogger&lt;/span&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://imgsli.com/MTgzMzgx" target="_blank"&gt;Lookout Landing with various Weather&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://imgsli.com/MTgzMzk1" target="_blank"&gt;Sky Islands&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://imgsli.com/MTgzNDY2" target="_blank"&gt;Cave Example&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://imgsli.com/MTgzNDY3" target="_blank"&gt;Shrines&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://imgsli.com/MTgzMzky" target="_blank"&gt;Depths&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://imgsli.com/MTgzMzkw" target="_blank"&gt;Faron Jungle&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://imgsli.com/MTgzMzg2" target="_blank"&gt;Hebra Peaks&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://imgsli.com/MTgzMzg0" target="_blank"&gt;Gerudo Desert, Day&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://imgsli.com/MTgzMzg1" target="_blank"&gt;Gerudo Desert, Night&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://imgsli.com/MTgzMzgz" target="_blank"&gt;Zora's Domain&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://imgsli.com/MTgzMzg3" target="_blank"&gt;Goron City&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://imgsli.com/MTgzMzg5" target="_blank"&gt;Forest&lt;br&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://imgsli.com/MTgzODA1" target="_blank"&gt;Gerudo Story Area&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://imgsli.com/MTg0NjA1" target="_blank"&gt;Castle Pit&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://imgsli.com/MTg0NjA2" target="_blank"&gt;Restored Post-Intro Area&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://imgsli.com/MTg0NjA3" target="_blank"&gt;Optional Interior Add-on&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;u&gt;Overview:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Not removing all fog is intentional.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Increases visibility during all weather patterns.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Increases visibility in Shrines and Caves.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Restores the Post-Intro version of "Beneath the Castle"&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Does not affect the Depths.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Does not affect Thunderhead Isles (game design reasons).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Does not affect distant mountain ranges, steep cliffs, etc.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Does not affect bloom, dust, clouds, or other particle effects.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Does not affect any Interiors unless you use the Interior Add-on.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Bonus: The Dark Title Screen variant hides the mural background.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;u&gt;General:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;You need both the Base Defogger and the Interior Add-on &lt;i&gt;&lt;u&gt;if you want the effect of both&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/i&gt;. They are packaged separately because the Interior Add-on must be updated to work with game updates. &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;The Base Defogger works on all updates. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;For the Interior Add-on &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;you must&lt;/span&gt; use the version that is meant for the Game Update you're currently playing on. Using the wrong version of the Interior Add-on will lead to complications. &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Game Update 1.2.1, 1.4.0 (and newer) might still work with the 1.2.0 Interior Add-on. Give it a try.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Please make sure no other mods alter &lt;u&gt;Bootup.Nin_NX_NVN.pack.zs&lt;/u&gt; or the Interior Add-on will no longer work correctly or it may break your other mod that includes it.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;u&gt;Troubleshooting Issues:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Please disable all mods and ReShade if in use.&lt;/span&gt; If there is a conflict with a mod or the coloration is off because of ReShade, or if there is a bug with the emulator you're using, these are things that I cannot fix for you.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Users have been using this on their Switch successfully, if you get a fatal Atmosphere error, this isn't something I can diagnose or fix. You will need to try on your own.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;u&gt;Installation Steps for Base Defogger&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Switch 1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;You must be on Atmosphere 1.5.4 or newer.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Extract the &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;romfs&lt;/span&gt; folder into ...&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;sd://atmosphere/contents/0100F2C0115B6000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Create the 0100F2C0115B6000 folder if it doesn't exist.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;del&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Switch 2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;del&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;TBD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Ry*jinx / Ry*bing / Kenji-NX&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Right-click the game in your game list and select ...&lt;br&gt;　○ &lt;span class="GreenColor SelectedElement"&gt;Open Mods Directory&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unzip and then place the &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;entire included&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt; folder&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; into this directory.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Mods located here are found and loaded automatically.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;If&#13;
 you encounter any issues, try using 7zip to extract the &#13;
mod. Otherwise, reconsider your &#13;
emulator setup. Try disabling all other mods and check what's happening. Check for conflicts.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;For &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Ry*bing / Kenji-NX&lt;/span&gt;, they might include a mod management section.&lt;br&gt;You will need to make sure the mod is enabled if so.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Y*zu / Eden&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Right-click the game in your game list and select ...&lt;br&gt;　○ &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Mod Data Location&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unzip and then place the &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;entire included&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt; folder&lt;/span&gt; into this directory.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Right-click the game ► Properties menu, ensure the mod is enabled.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;If&#13;
 you encounter any issues, try using 7zip to extract the &#13;
mod. Otherwise, reconsider your &#13;
emulator setup. Try disabling all other mods and check what's happening. Check for conflicts.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;For &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Eden&lt;/span&gt;, they might change in the UI where mods are managed.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Interior Add-on Installation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Same steps as the Base Defogger.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
