      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/683e46da7caab.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/683e4f40a2075.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/683e46dfc5cb1.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/683e46e50951b.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/683e46eb5ad58.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/683e46f10682c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/683e46f33abf3.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/683e46f65f7db.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/683e46f9d72c2.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/683e4701746be.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/683e470546e48.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/683e4707e26ad.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/683e470a3bc8e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/683e470f2e7e9.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6854e616e529b.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Dragon Gliders&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Demon Lord Gleeok from Challenge Mode has been added!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;Replaces Link's paraglider with fully animated rideable dragons!&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Features:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Two flight modes (with and without shield)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Dynamic dragon motion (helps with FOV)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Multiple dragon types available in two sizes&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Recommended:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Start a shield surf animation (ZL+A) mid air and pull out your glider&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Very slightly tilt joystick forward to enable dynamic dragon motion&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Enable Glider Speed x3 (via cheats with TOTK Optimizer or TKMM)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Use Glider Speed cheat (tap A) with dynamic dragon motion&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Manually install the “All in One” TKMM file&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Optional:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Infinite stamina cheat for extended flight&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Moon jump cheat for upward gliding&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/480138"&gt;Ultracam mod&lt;/a&gt; (by&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class="MemberLink" href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2745192" data-id="member_2745192"&gt;MaxLastBreath&lt;/a&gt;) or other FOV mods&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This is mod is easily compatible with other animation mods with TKMM.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;UPDATE:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li class="SelectedElement"&gt;Demon Lord Gleeok from Challenge Mode has been added!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Demon Lord Gleeok is only compatible with Challenge Mode&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Use TKMM to merge mods together&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
